Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.06,0:01:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来替你擦背…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以进来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？不行 小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.17,0:01:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是为了薰的话 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵是认真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.41,0:01:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么我进来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等 不能进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.61,0:02:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿着衣服啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.59,0:02:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 不行就是不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀……！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.41,0:02:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.25,0:02:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个…禽兽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在对葵大小姐做什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等 住手 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.72,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅…雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三话  别离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好疼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.67,0:02:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我叫得太大声了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧 我也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来…这个人是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神乐崎 雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.22,0:03:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是从小就在身边照顾我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.89,0:03:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐 你明白自己在做什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.03,0:03:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有什么『但是』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要生气？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是跟家人联络过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多住几天也没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 实际上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是背着家人出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.68,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐请务必明确地理解自己的立场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,樱庭家自从樱庭和服店创业以来已经两百多年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.36,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在经营着国内有名的大企业樱庭集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是声名显赫的名门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能有辱樱庭这个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.37,0:04:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平常行动必须小心谨慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于私自离家出走 是我的不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是薰的未婚妻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.24,0:04:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 这个人和花菱家已经没有任何关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.12,0:04:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐的丈夫将成为樱庭集团的社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.36,0:04:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 葵大小姐必须和匹配的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个人被逐出花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.37,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与樱庭家已经没有关系了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.37,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样什么能力也没有 平庸的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与葵大小姐根本不配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么 葵大小姐现在立刻回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐 适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想离开薰的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.53,0:05:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法跟薰以外的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了成为薰的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而走过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够回去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要回到花菱家 我们就能在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.18,0:05:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请回来吧 薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我无法回花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰…薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.03,0:06:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是这样的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您父母亲都在担心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 再给我点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们两人最后再说几句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.85,0:06:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你 话说完毕 我一定回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能再见到薰 真的感到很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.05,0:07:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然小时候的薰也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是现在的薰比想象中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还要温柔、亲切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能这样在一起的话是多么幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.86,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 因为这是薰决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这也没有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我离开花菱家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.99,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因为我本来就不是花菱家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我原来的名字是本條薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.29,0:07:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母亲本條久美 父亲花菱优二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并没有正式的结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为花菱家的人强烈反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 在我五岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲死于交通事故后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的态度就突然变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望领养我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母亲为了不让我受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.12,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便事事按照花菱家的安排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我也不想让母亲担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直扮演着花菱的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我没法成为花菱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女人半年前就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还去想已经死掉的人干嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.18,0:08:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种女人 快点忘掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.89,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想反抗我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那个给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.94,0:09:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个…顽固的…家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本没有身为拥有三百年历史的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱家继承者的自觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有把你养育成人的恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是想要恩将仇报吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那以后我就决心离开花菱家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个是母亲给我的护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这个总算是保存到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里面放着我的脐带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这个是母亲最后留下的遗物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.21,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经没有所谓的家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里不是家 而是监牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.42,0:09:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我不会再回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.53,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.45,0:10:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵的手…真温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.58,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让人怀念的… 让人安心的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 就像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐 我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能一直待在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.46,0:11:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.26,0:11:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 我不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要想那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然过来找你是我不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.44,0:11:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饭要好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要勉强自己 好好保重身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要用这样担心的眼神看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.59,0:12:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…真的不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为薰你是我一直最喜欢的薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请以后也像现在一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像现在的我最喜欢的薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打搅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 花菱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.94,0:13:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 花菱 要一起去吃饭吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 花菱 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.51,0:13:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花菱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才我联络过您的父母亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们都非常担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再做这种轻率的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵大小姐万一出了什么事的话 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.95,0:14:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.78,0:14:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经没有所谓的家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.65,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是不在好 我在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰就会回忆起花菱家的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.67,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈 到哪里去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.84,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子？真子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.89,0:15:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰此后就一直一个人了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.65,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这间房子有这么宽敞吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.49,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锅里和冰箱里有昨晚的剩菜 请早点吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.73,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还以为已经习惯了自己一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.72,0:16:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么…为什么 会这样…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.57,0:16:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.24,0:16:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请在吡一声后留下姓名与留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰对不起 在你出门的时间里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.56,0:17:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵？  薰 太好了 你在家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.69,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 小葵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我想再见一次薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想把一些事情告诉薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.24,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以从雅那里逃出来了 但是迷了路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃出来…小葵 现在在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.58,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想是在跟薰相遇的车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.19,0:17:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 立刻就去 绝对别从那里离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没…她还没回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.75,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 该跟薰怎么说好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要怎样去面对他呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然还是添麻烦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.03,0:18:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只会给薰添麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自地跑过来见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自地进到他家打扫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又擅自地叫他出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰可能不会原谅这样的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可能很生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可能已经被薰讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.67,0:19:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…有很多话要跟薰说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 在等薰的这段时间里我想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想 是不是给薰添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我还是不能不说 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.01,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去吧…回家去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.28,0:20:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很冷吧 洗澡水热好了 先洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…薰湿的比较严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.66,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没关系 你先洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟薰分开后 想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雅说的话 樱庭家的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.61,0:20:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有父母亲的事 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要离开樱庭家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使舍弃一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想要和薰在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.06,0:21:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.33,0:21:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.33,0:21:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我以薰的妻子的身份 跟您缔结婚约吧
